poem-sTETKXl0tUNMHQSfVPqeGQ">Tây Sơn thi hoạ giả tam thập dư nhân, tái dụng tiền vận vi tạ - 西山詩和者三十餘人，再用前韻為謝</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/author-ZsPeAEZWTH-jxxg2cYfLgg">Tô Thức</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/Th%C3%A1i-B%C3%ACnh-nh%C3%A0n-v%E1%BB%8Bnh/poem-S53ljpnPzF1kzQFwvr9m_w">Thái Bình nhàn vịnh - 太平閑咏</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/author-14GcnhLjD2ajP0MTgtX13Q">Ngô Thì Nhậm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/Th%C3%A1i-tang-t%E1%BB%AD/poem-kEtJEG_ZpvOqTp5qubCKUQ">Thái tang tử - 採桑子</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/author-ZsPeAEZWTH-jxxg2cYfLgg">Tô Thức</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/Th%C6%B0-th%E1%BB%8B-b%E1%BA%A1n-t%E1%BB%91ng-L%C3%BD-Hi%E1%BA%BFn-Ki%E1%BB%81u/poem-XtPE7j8i3zxf9M0tgrz13Q">Thư thị bạn tống Lý Hiến Kiều - 書示伴送李憲喬</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/author-14GcnhLjD2ajP0MTgtX13Q">Ngô Thì Nhậm</a>)<br></div>	</div>
